extendedInfo.description: Think you look famous? Maybe you look like one of the guys of one direction? or maybe like the movie star George ClooneyMaybe have a famous double? Now is you chance to find your caricature look a like!Easily upload your photo and let us take care of the rest! We will find the caricature that looks exactly like you! :)Find your match!!Many characters are featured in this app including:Rihanna, Kristen Stewart (Twilight), Shakira, Jennifer Lopez, Britney Spears, Beyonce, Katy Perry, Sandra Bullock, Jennifer Aniston. Adele, Belen, Jessica Simpson. Johnny Depp, Harry Potter, Michael Jackson Silvio Berlusconi, Burns (Simpson), Barrack Obama, Dr. House, Messi, Justin Bieber, Albert Einstein, George Clooney, Marylin Manson, Mario Balotelli, Tom Cruise, Brad Pitt, Miley Cyrus, Taylor Swift,Cameron Diaz, Angelina Jolie, Penelope Cruz, Paris Hilton, Lady Gaga, Rihanna, Kristen Stewart (Twilight), Shakira, Jennifer Lopez, Britney Spears, Beyonce, Katy Perry, Sandra Bullock, Jennifer Aniston. Adele, Belen, Jessica Simpson.This is only caricatures and not real images of the actors mentioned, in full respect of the rules of copyright and privacy.In order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application. This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service. Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps. You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you
